            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arco</ex></expan> Pontio <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arci</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilio</ex></expan> Palatina <lb n="2"/>Eglecto <note>sic</note> Archelao <expan><abbr>c</abbr><ex>larissimo</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>iro</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>cons</abbr><ex>uli</ex></expan> curatori Cartha<lb break="no" n="4"/>ginis unicae bonitatis <lb n="5"/>et gravitatis viro patro<lb break="no" n="6"/>no inconparabili <note>sic</note> <lb n="7"/>Valerii Philostorgus <lb n="8"/>senior et iunior clientes foti <lb n="9"/>semper eius auxilis
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>(B): Cantarelli, AE 1916, Fornari, AE 1917/18: abweichende Textwiedergabe.</p>
            </div>
